{"tid":882041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍運-9偵察機進入日本「防空識別區」","createTime":"2018-10-30T01:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T14:14:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"79e2c09c3cc8ff019a17ecc61f22e45644d57f5b","tid":882041,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181030/large/1540862499_8ccb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181030%2Flarge%2F1540862499_8ccb.jpg&h=2f437ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據日本防衞省統合幕僚監部發佈的消息稱，昨日（29日）一架中國運-9電子偵察機進入日本「防空識別區」，並穿越對馬海峽往返東海日本海，日本及南韓分別緊急出動戰機，跟蹤監視。<br />\n<br />\n這是進入10月份以來，中國軍機首次出現在日本附近空域，也是自8月份中國運-9電子偵察機再次穿越對馬海峽往返東海日本海。從日本統合幕僚監部公佈的飛行路線圖來看，此次運-9電子偵察機是沿着靠近日本列島一側穿越的對馬海峽，早於8月時，運-9電子偵察機則是沿着靠近朝鮮半島一側完成的穿越。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，南韓聯合參謀本部稱，一架解放軍運-9電子偵察機於當地時間上午10時03分左右進入南韓「防空識別區」，在後續飛行期間又多次進出南韓「防空識別區」，直到下午3時02分許才飛離南韓防空識別區，在近5個小時的飛行期間，中國軍機有2小時是在南韓「防空識別區」範圍內飛行，而南韓空軍則出動F-15K和F-16戰鬥機跟蹤監視中國軍機。韓方還指出，這是中國軍機今年第6次進入南韓「防空識別區」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181030/58851800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851800&d=UgOTwj4WJrJn7233pRlQ3f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=12c7e945\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851800&h=2214cf47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181030/58851800</a>"},{"pid":"78823cf3feaccf21890fea293180b0a684daedf6","tid":882041,"uid":9050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"運狗偵察機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b2607b0a697d4714a5f5d61940bfe3a40543f8","tid":882041,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國軍機有2小時是在南韓「防空識別區」範圍內飛行，而南韓空軍則出動F-15K和F-16戰鬥機跟蹤監視中國軍機。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住支那呢D垃圾<br />\n<br />\n出TA-50就得<br />\n<br />\nF-15K和F-16係地面stand by<br />\n<br />\n慳油慳錢"},{"pid":"8623641d53bb6df792026d1b3b39f533c1841760","tid":882041,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"攔截支那廢機任務, <br />\n<br />\n可以用慳錢慳油既機就得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/TA-50-_Group_Display_in_ROKAF_Airbase.jpg/1920px-TA-50-_Group_Display_in_ROKAF_Airbase.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F5%2F5e%2FTA-50-_Group_Display_in_ROKAF_Airbase.jpg%2F1920px-TA-50-_Group_Display_in_ROKAF_Airbase.jpg&h=a347e8ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c67ee2482272d5f508116a6d3229664a8b61257f","tid":882041,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"掛個ECM JAM死佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://data3.primeportal.net/hangar/bill_spidle3/alq-131v/images/alq-131v_10_of_10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdata3.primeportal.net%2Fhangar%2Fbill_spidle3%2Falq-131v%2Fimages%2Falq-131v_10_of_10.jpg&h=81a5288e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d094cce005afb98f9eab119763bb382a62f76906","tid":882041,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"個識別區有咩意思？見住佢衝入都唔打落嚟，防乜鬼空"},{"pid":"ebe657b822a8e2edb0e2a24d624322ea90718e42","tid":882041,"uid":103513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d094cce005afb98f9eab119763bb382a62f76906","tid":882041,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"個識別區有咩意思？見住佢衝入都唔打落嚟，防乜鬼空"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"防空識別區（英語：Air Defense Identification Zone，縮寫：ADIZ），是指的是一國基於空防需要，單方面所劃定的空域，以利軍方迅速定位管制，最先由美國提出。防空識別區與飛航情報區並不一樣，所劃定的區域也不一定相同。[1]<br />\n防空識別區是國家依自身安全需要劃分，沒有國際法效力，其範圍大於領空，<span style=\"color: red;\">飛行器若是進入某國防空識別區內，需要進行識別、告知動作</span>。這個國家則判斷飛行器有無攻擊、危險性質，若無危險性且停留時間短，則會進行勸告、了解動作；若是停留時間長，則有可能驅離[2]。一般而言，一國對飛行器的定位、監視和管制，是在飛行器進入該國防空識別區之後，而非之前。通常情況下，若飛行器進入一國的防空識別區，該國可以採取某種方式，如起飛戰鬥機監視飛行器，<span style=\"color: red;\">但在飛行器進入該國領空前，無權迫降、擊落該飛行器，否則將嚴重違反國際法</span>。"},{"pid":"4e53cff2a7cf44080e9f5b4d483ba3800ce0fbbe","tid":882041,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d094cce005afb98f9eab119763bb382a62f76906","tid":882041,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"個識別區有咩意思？見住佢衝入都唔打落嚟，防乜鬼空"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"識別區唔同領空，最多可以驅趕"},{"pid":"951669dea75f17fbfd8f3e8627ddeabe67fc04bc","tid":882041,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"救命一日射左幾次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9898db355c63ee822b98317a48f6cbfadfc191","tid":882041,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"點解日本唔得閒派返架偵察機去東海行下"}]}